videos.description: Georgia Tech misses the dunk, but the offensive rebound gets pushed to Tadric Jackson for the 3-pointer, as the Yellow Jackets are heating up near the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Jackson helping spark 15-2 run

videos.description: Bonzie Colson takes the pass from Matt Farrell and converts the tough lay-in.
videos.headline: Colson helping Notre Dame storm back in second half

videos.description: Ben Lammers hits the jumper to build on Georgia Tech's second half lead, as the Yellow Jackets try to stave off Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Ben Lammers heating up for Georgia Tech

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson hits the jumper, earning 25 points on the game, which is a new career high.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson earns career high in points

videos.description: Ben Lammers gets the defensive rebound for Georgia Tech, but throws it to Notre Dame's Matt Farrell, who converts from beyond the arc.
videos.headline: Lammers' turnover leads to 3-pointer for Notre Dame

videos.description: Off the Notre Dame miss, Georgia Tech gets it to Josh Okogie, who hits the layup at the buzzer to give the Yellow Jackets a 62-60 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One Play (Georgia Tech wins at the buzzer) 2017/01/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia Tech wins at the buzzer

videos.description: Tadric Jackson talks about the final rebound that led to Georgia Tech's game-winning buzzer beater.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson discusses big performance and final sequence

videos.description: Tadric Jackson and Josh Okogie came up big in Georgia Tech's upset win over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Jackson, Okogie steer Georgia Tech to victory
